r />\n所以用建制左派建制右派講"},{"pid":"adb41add959ef8786258154857cb7398c600b9f3","tid":1913974,"uid":260603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:15:02.000Z","msg":"用納粹黨踢走共產黨<br />\n雖然效果不知道<br />\n亦未必對香港好<br />\n<br />\n不過我支持任何踢走共產黨及其走狗嘅方法<br />\n萬國聯手，殲滅中共"},{"pid":"faeb9e44eb341e9d771c984a39ee1791866754ba","tid":1913974,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"田少就係想夾住呢3席嚟脅迫政府"},{"pid":"8e0b302b7aa044c25ca20a822be92b780127bb5a","tid":1913974,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adb41add959ef8786258154857cb7398c600b9f3","tid":1913974,"uid":260603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:15:02.000Z","msg":"用納粹黨踢走共產黨<br />\n雖然效果不知道<br />\n亦未必對香港好<br />\n<br />\n不過我支持任何踢走共產黨及其走狗嘅方法<br />\n萬國聯手，殲滅中共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:16:15.000Z","msg":"yes<br />\n不要政治潔癖<br />\n團結一切可以團結既人<br />\n我地作為弱勢既一方咁先贏得到"},{"pid":"181efe91ed38dc2c5a7e9f6e30e3800046ef6e91","tid":1913974,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef751ada2ad71fce068aa67340c76f25da6f5480","tid":1913974,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"96e1c4a85431cdb9aedeb428bd0346970aa1ff8a","tid":1913974,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:12:18.000Z","msg":"鬍鬚同田少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你以為佢地會唔聽支共話？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"佢背後係誠哥丫嘛<br />\n誠哥比阿習背後插咁多刀你估佢聽唔聽共產黨話？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:16:19.000Z","msg":"背後係誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好咁天真"},{"pid":"b93fe2ec3255febc61048709dad9b9a5cb7f684b","tid":1913974,"uid":268591,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:17:05.000Z","msg":"曾鈺成你都信？！你醒未呀？！"},